# Per-build environment file.
#
# bma-setup-workstation copies this to `.env` on first clone. Add buyer-product-
# specific variables here as the build needs them; the workstation skill never
# overwrites an existing .env.
#
# Examples (uncomment and fill in as the build requires):
# SECRET_KEY=
# DATABASE_URL=
# FLASK_DEBUG=0
# PORT=5000
